will enter total income, you will prompt user to enter the choice for tax rebate and amount utilize
in that section and you will calculate eligible amount for the tax rebate
1. donation (max eligible amount 100000) and rebate is 2%
2. insurance (max eligible amount 50000) and rebate is 2.5%
3. education (max eligible amount 150000) and rebate is 3%
4. loan (max eligible amount 120000) and rebate is 3%
